review:
Enjoying it so far.  It is a bit challenging even if it is just normal mode but that's ok.  

A few suggestions:
1. When I applied the 'not owned' filter, it is still showing some cards I owned, not sure whether that is a bug that needs a fix;
2. Will be helpful if a filter by rarity is available;
3. Will be helpful to add a clear deck button instead of having to delete and create new every time if I want to keep the same heroes;

Cheers!
